 the contrary"},{"pid":"f2140de59ffcf3f162a871e10a2e444420d657db","tid":454416,"uid":34755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港隊攞世界盃先定閉門先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雲加俾人炒先定閉門先？"},{"pid":"ef0073df20dc499b428993463771ec91c7e9ed9c","tid":454416,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>sorry可能我眼殘 球隊踢波 球迷噓歌 啲錢係罰邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不嬲都罰足總啦</blockquote><br />\n好有趣既規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc90d44e4fd205f78d4f23f332b874a64a13864","tid":454416,"uid":76776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:26:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbf7ab23f2f89f2cfed7a3e2dcf20986207bebbb","tid":454416,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:32:25.000Z","msg":"通常噓人地國歌 或者種族歧視某國藉球員 球隊大條道理不滿同足總會懲罰<br />\n咁噓自己國歌呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  港隊會唔會嘈生哂 表示不滿 而"},{"pid":"dd696f655e7e3ec755c92238f6d74fbd9de44536","tid":454416,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:33:01.000Z","msg":"通常噓人地國歌 或者種族歧視某國藉球員 球隊大條道理不滿同足總會懲罰<br />\n咁噓自己國歌呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  港隊會唔會嘈生哂 表示不滿 而足總又罰番自己 例如扣分呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}